  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/8d42fefbec8f8711fc14c130d7c03997.poster.avif?t=1744899219\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/8d42fefbec8f8711fc14c130d7c03997.webm?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/8d42fefbec8f8711fc14c130d7c03997.mp4?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Summary</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzle Dazzle is a unique, addictive and breathtaking take on the classic block puzzle game formula. The synchronization of energizing music and gorgeous art creates a mesmerizing and intense overall experience. Enjoy the banging music, calming melodies, reactive backgrounds and spectacular special effects while strategically matching blocks and completing objectives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/6d7aaec7e6c36f8d7f66714ab45ebc47.poster.avif?t=1744899219\" width=720 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/6d7aaec7e6c36f8d7f66714ab45ebc47.webm?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/6d7aaec7e6c36f8d7f66714ab45ebc47.mp4?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 Arcade Mode: Dive into a Visual Extravaganza!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have curated 50 unique levels set in surreal landscapes. Each level is a visual feast with an extraordinary blend of graphics and gameplay, making Arcade Mode a true celebration of sensory delight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌐 Survival Mode: Rise to the Top of the Leaderboard!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete against the clock as you strive to surpass global competitors and secure your spot at the pinnacle of the leaderboard. Endurance meets strategy in this mode, providing an adrenaline-pumping experience that will keep you coming back for more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/fd86fadda96000cab8e5e8cbc663f1f1.poster.avif?t=1744899219\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/fd86fadda96000cab8e5e8cbc663f1f1.webm?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/fd86fadda96000cab8e5e8cbc663f1f1.mp4?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ Handcrafted Levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Game Modes to Play </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full Controller Support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Leaderboards and Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Cloud</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Deck Compatible</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/8d42fefbec8f8711fc14c130d7c03997.poster.avif?t=1744899219\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/8d42fefbec8f8711fc14c130d7c03997.webm?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/8d42fefbec8f8711fc14c130d7c03997.mp4?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Summary</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzle Dazzle is a unique, addictive and breathtaking take on the classic block puzzle game formula. The synchronization of energizing music and gorgeous art creates a mesmerizing and intense overall experience. Enjoy the banging music, calming melodies, reactive backgrounds and spectacular special effects while strategically matching blocks and completing objectives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/6d7aaec7e6c36f8d7f66714ab45ebc47.poster.avif?t=1744899219\" width=720 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/6d7aaec7e6c36f8d7f66714ab45ebc47.webm?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/6d7aaec7e6c36f8d7f66714ab45ebc47.mp4?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 Arcade Mode: Dive into a Visual Extravaganza!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have curated 50 unique levels set in surreal landscapes. Each level is a visual feast with an extraordinary blend of graphics and gameplay, making Arcade Mode a true celebration of sensory delight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌐 Survival Mode: Rise to the Top of the Leaderboard!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete against the clock as you strive to surpass global competitors and secure your spot at the pinnacle of the leaderboard. Endurance meets strategy in this mode, providing an adrenaline-pumping experience that will keep you coming back for more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/fd86fadda96000cab8e5e8cbc663f1f1.poster.avif?t=1744899219\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/fd86fadda96000cab8e5e8cbc663f1f1.webm?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/fd86fadda96000cab8e5e8cbc663f1f1.mp4?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ Handcrafted Levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Game Modes to Play </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full Controller Support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Leaderboards and Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Cloud</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Deck Compatible</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
